snippet.title: Katsl - alpha gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
After 5 months of silent development, we are happy to bring you a new Trailer for Katsl, a cozy game where you build cute towns for cats, to help them reach their hopes and dreams.

Wishlist us on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/2631780?utm_source=youtube_Katsl&utm_campaign=Trailers&utm_media=TrailerV3
